Subject: [PATCH 6/6] =?UTF-8?q?feat(qwen3-tts):=20fp8=20text=5Fembedding?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20(native=20kernel=20path)=20=E2=80=94=20~311MB=20VRAM,=20no?=
