MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Load text_embedding as FP8 e4m3 + FP32 per-group scales when present (classified by
dtype; FP16 stays backward-compatible), and attach scales at the 5 text-embedding
lookup sites via scalesFor() (keys off kFP8 dtype). Uses the existing sm_87-portable
Fp8EmbeddingLoader (cuda_fp8.h software convert; SUPPORTS_FP8 is CUDA>=11.8 gated, not arch).
+ scripts/quantize_text_embedding_fp8.py (block=128, e4m3, matches kernel dequant).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

